Initial commit: Multi-source notification agent

Features:
- Email monitoring via IMAP (multiple accounts)
- RSS feed support
- LLM-powered summarization (OpenAI compatible)
- SMS notifications via Twilio
- Email notifications via SMTP
- SQLite-based state management
- Automatic scheduling (cron/launchd)
- Time-based filtering (only new emails since last run)

Architecture:
- Clean Python package structure
- Configurable via environment variables
- Production-ready error handling
- Comprehensive logging

Documentation:
- README with setup instructions
- AWS architecture design for multi-tenant deployment
- Deployment plan for AWS
- Local setup guide for macOS

Security:
- No hardcoded credentials
- .env file excluded from git
- Database files excluded from git
